gameRecap.title: Game Recap: Wizards 113, Grizzlies 106
gameRecap.excerpt: The Wizards defeated the Grizzlies, 113-106. Jordan Poole led all scorers with 27 points (8-23 FG), along with four rebounds and two assists for the Wizards, while Corey Kispert (22 points, five 3PM) and Kyle Kuzma (21 points, 13 rebounds) added a combined 43 points in the victory. Desmond Bane tallied 26 points (4-10 3PM) and five assists for the Grizzlies in the losing effort. The Wizards improve to 1-1 on the season, while the Grizzlies fall to 0-3.
